The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Ralf to race for Toyota
Berlin: Ralf Schumacher has given a clear indication he will race for Toyota next season with an official announcement due at this weekends British Grand Prix, according to a German magazine interview released on Tuesday. Bunte asked Ralf if he could confirm he would be joining Toyota, to which the current Williams driver replied: Bingo! The decision about my future has been settled for a long time. It will be announced at Silverstone on July 11. If, according to your information I am joining Toyota, I can confirm Bunte is not totally off the mark. His managers declined to comment on the prospective move to Toyota. (Reuters)  Copyright 
